## Frequently Asked Questions

### How do I create a photo book?
Open the app, choose your photos, customize your layout, and preview your book before placing an order.

### Can I edit my book after creating it?
Yes, you can modify your book at any time before completing your order.

### What if I experience an issue?
Please contact us at contact@albu-me.com with details about your issue, and we’ll assist you as soon as possible.

